OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHow 175 British children   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwere infected with HIV     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, More than 150 children with the blood  
OL,6, disorder haemophilia were infected with
OL,7, HIV in the 1980s, according to         
OL,8, documents from the national archives   
OL,9, seen by BBC News. Some of the families 
OL,10, affected are giving evidence at a      
OL,11, public inquiry into what has been      
OL,12, called the worst treatment disaster in 
OL,13, the history of the NHS.                
OL,15,FIt was almost 36 years ago - in late   
OL,16,FOctober 1986 - but Linda will never    
OL,17,Fforget the day she was told her son had
OL,18,Fbeen infected.                         
